{"tid":1630594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝勇武，多謝和理非！","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:59:12.000Z","uid":110142,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c09c89cd9f40452376e2da78972cd375914b468b","tid":1630594,"uid":110142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"今日雖然比人拉左好多個，<br />\n亦有啲唔完善嘅地方，<br />\n但我地不分化不割蓆！<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位和理非肯走出來！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝各位勇武手足保護我地，幫大家頂住，甚到因為咁犧牲左！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次大家記得留定退路比手足撤！<br />\n勇武保護我地，我地都要識保護翻佢地！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆</span></span>"}]}